public static Domain parseDomain(java.lang.String s,
                                 int startNum,
                                 java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.util.List<Domain>> domains)
Parse a domain and their parents from a string. The string should be a dot-delimited sequence of domains, first one being the root

Parameters:
s - parseable string
domains - a map of previously parsed domains, which can be used as parents. This will be extended with new domains found
